"*%s (IA)* Lanceremo un attacco massiccio contro %s in %d turno per "
"impedirgli il lancio della nave spaziale."
msgstr[1] ""
"*%s (IA)* Lanceremo un attacco massiccio contro %s in %d turni per "
"impedirgli il lancio della nave spaziale."

#: ai/advdiplomacy.c:1275
#, c-format
msgid ""
"*%s (AI)* Your aid in this matter will be expected. Long live our glorious "
"alliance!"
msgstr ""
"*%s (IA)* È atteso il vostro aiuto in questa faccenda. Lunga vita alla "
"nostra gloriosa alleanza!"

#: ai/advdiplomacy.c:1281
#, c-format
msgid ""
"*%s (AI)* %s has grossly violated his treaties with us for own gain.  We "
"will answer in force in %d turn and expect you to honour your alliance with "
"us and do likewise!"
msgid_plural ""
"*%s (AI)* %s has grossly violated his treaties with us for own gain.  We "
"will answer in force in %d turns and expect you to honour your alliance with "
"us and do likewise!"
